data.description: Newly installed PGT hurricane impact windows & slider on this concrete block home!!!  Impact windows & slider were permitted, approved, and permit closed!  $30K+ for hurricane windows/slider. No sitting in the dark with metal shutters!  Neighborhood sits high above the road!  Roof new in 2020!  Brand new water heater!!!  Bathrooms remodeled!  Porcelain tile in Master Bathroom!  Kitchen redone with new cabinets & countertops!  Home has separate living room & family room! Space not wasted on hallways! Vaulted ceilings in Living Areas. Screened trussed patio! ALL bedrooms have walk-in closets! Tile throughout home! Ceiling fans in all bedrooms, living room, and family room!  No neighbors backing up directly to your lot!  Lot backs up to one of the oversized canals in Palm Bay that the city keeps clean!  Check out aerial photos!  No HOA!!!  City Water!!!  Quick access to St Johns Heritage Parkway! Selling As-Is, Inspections Welcome!
